{
  "stem": "19969.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 63.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, well, you've been a damn fine soldier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, I don't need any explanation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, you go on back to your unit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The whole interview lasted no more than a minute or two minutes, maybe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I saluted and left and went back to my Munich-- my unit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then I found out the inspector general, in the meantime, was conducting a very thorough investigation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What a strange thing, nobody-- when the report came out that I found just a few years ago, it said that I was not available.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's not true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was not there the first few days, but I came back and was back a good 10 days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was available all the time, but nobody ever said hello or goodbye to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And after I'd been back about 10 days, and I got orders then to report to Rheims, to [INAUDIBLE] headquarters, and that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then from there, I came on back to the States, got back in August of 1945.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But I was always curious as to what happened in that investigation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was told from various sources that the investigator-- that Patton had stopped the investigation and ordered the whole thing dismissed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as the years went on, none of us who were at Dachau ever talked much about it until they started this Holocaust Memorial week, various states did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I begun to hear of claims by the 42nd Infantry Division that they were the first in Dachau and the ones who liberated it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, that surprised me considerably.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I knew that they had been there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
